abstract: Tottenham Hotspur defeats Arsenal, 2-1; other soccer scores noted.
snippet: Arsenal sustained its fourth loss in the Premier League, losing at Tottenham, and Frank Lampard’s three goals helped Chelsea rout Bolton, 5-1.
lead_paragraph: Arsenal sustained its fourth loss in the Premier League, losing at Tottenham, and Frank Lampard’s three goals helped Chelsea rout Bolton, 5-1.
